
;頭撫で（複雑になってもいいよう関数分け）
@VISIT_STROKING_HEAD_MESSAGE

PRINTFORML You gently pat %CALLNAME%'s head...
CALL KOJO_PRINT("訪問","頭撫で")
IF CFLAG:崩壊
	PRINTFORML %CALLNAME% stares at you will dull eyes...
	
ELSEIF CFLAG:乳牛 || CFLAG:洗脳 || ＃陥落状態／隷属＃
	PRINTFORML %CALLNAME%'s face flushes red and she starts heavily breathing,
	PRINTFORML as she wonders what's to come...
	
ELSEIF ＃陥落状態／恋慕以上＃ || GROUPMATCH(CSTR:状態／あなたの子,"成長中","成長後")
	PRINTFORML %CALLNAME% narrows her eyes in pleasure...
ELSEIF ＃陥落状態／陥落以上＃
	PRINTFORML %CALLNAME% quietly enjoys the sensation...
ELSEIF ＃陥落状態／屈服以上＃
	PRINTFORML %CALLNAME% is conflicted. She doesn't want this, but it feels quite good...
ELSE
	PRINTFORML %CALLNAME% doesn't seem to enjoy it...
ENDIF



